{"tid":1496564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚風向如下","createTime":"2019-08-22T14:47:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T21:45:28.000Z","uid":208722,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"09fe366bf7b186d2125f033b3188c73bbe5ceff2","tid":1496564,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:47:57.000Z","msg":"因為聽日要組人鏈<br />\n<br />\n所以今晚都吹緊風，好多都話聽晚去「識囡、拖人手、食女」，而另一個人就唱雙簧話啲人去到都係做厹，唔會出席，想從而抹黑個運動，減低其他人出去嘅意欲<br />\n<br />\n已經係和理非活動，事前重要畀波羅的海三國傳媒注視，點都要似返個樣啦下嘛？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">都兩個幾月，好多事都係撫心自問，而唔係聽討論區一兩條友嘅說話去決定自己去唔去做，好冇？</span>"},{"pid":"8dd9a2d88849d25140e0c57a269d67913692798c","tid":1496564,"uid":47509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:48:43.000Z","msg":"聽日見"},{"pid":"8c0e3b8526887a83f2d61ba42fefbfab202165ad","tid":1496564,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991c3cf6c049c9fa8b15d84bcf87eb449ebf5bff","tid":1496564,"uid":299623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T14:55:16.000Z","msg":"屌 我都覺 等我聽晚落去同大家討論下"},{"pid":"1445912b0b83ebda78cdd3199f7dddbe1540e886","tid":1496564,"uid":122551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/UKtdBAJGK9I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FUKtdBAJGK9I&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2Ld%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=a1f00c92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/UKtdBAJGK9I</a>"},{"pid":"970866a7533ac05f835f54a9ecef36851ed97390","tid":1496564,"uid":122551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:05:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hr79GDYsIqc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fhr79GDYsIqc&d=eywEaFxHh3WcM61vPhP2Ld%2FmPfBwacFXLzUp2rw9Z8Q%3D&h=d3ad00d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hr79GDYsIqc</a>"},{"pid":"18fe1214cf4eed269346d10f2e41bcbec6d5790b","tid":1496564,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:06:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"111ec13c71b0062d400bc4d0d649c50214621617","tid":1496564,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:07:24.000Z","msg":"聽日見 最多戴手套"},{"pid":"eb5063cee6ad2c102d2746c0fb0491946e7d2a07","tid":1496564,"uid":268251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:08:20.000Z","msg":"講風向, 大家要小心, 因為共風向明顯變左.<br />\n經過網絡大軍既白痴表現, 中共知道對外文宣不可能勝利, 已經將注意力集中返係香港.<br />\n你睇下港鐵, 國泰, 就知道發生咩事. 黎緊下一步會係各大學院校, 中學校長, 甚至小學校長.<br />\n<br />\n不要掉以輕心, 香港係主戰場, 外國支持, 只能令佢唔出解放軍,<br />\n呢方面暫時係成功左, 但運動要成功都係要睇香港."},{"pid":"eae07c6e4ba5e2f7c96af91a06e765172da55ae2","tid":1496564,"uid":82183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:19:20.000Z","msg":"聽日見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oCZGwHK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoCZGwHK.jpg&h=a3a72d26&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"51280f3d374e71526119552fcce0dd1cb7b3d1b0","tid":1496564,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:22:16.000Z","msg":"[好戲量] 點解仲有人得閒理深夜d風向post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1486364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1486364</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c17cdf9a943a0bbef2fbf54501ce6844a022d765","tid":1496564,"uid":33495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce251246219bb1912703ace20b3ebd8b49d6886d","tid":1496564,"uid":279252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T16:24:17.000Z","msg":"聽日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76c3d0e9276d006268a9c590c64f580639aa2ff0","tid":1496564,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"